member.summary:
Get a reference of the row internal storage for the key..
This allows performance optimization as it saves the key lookup.
User should always lock the row before operations and release the lock at the end.
Usage example:
var st = Prime.SharedStorageService.GetUnsafeRowFromTable>SomeStructure>("key", Context.DUT);

using(st.Lock())
{
   st.Value.DoSomething();
}
.

